svg:svg.svg:desc:
This blank map of Japan is based on the geographical data opened for "Global Mapping" by Geographical Survay Institute of Japan.
Geographical Survay Institute of Japan: http://www1.gsi.go.jp/geowww/globalmap-gsi/download/index.html
International Steering Comittee for Global Mapping: http://www.iscgm.org/cgi-bin/fswiki/wiki.cgi
The original data was rendered and traced by freehand to create this map.
Kabipan-Otoko
